items.sentence: Neither Tom nor Mary has done anything foolish.
Neither Tom nor Mary has been working overtime.
Neither Tom nor Mary has been very cooperative.
Neither Tom nor Mary has been very busy lately.
Neither Tom nor Mary has been skipping classes.
Tom has been trying to learn a few card tricks.
Tom got caught stealing from the cash register.
Tom ended up doing what he said he wouldn't do.
Tom doesn't really have the courage to do that.
Tom doesn't really enjoy doing that by himself.
